         <gmd:abstract>
            <gco:CharacterString>This raster layer shows the Urban Heat Island Effect in 11 European CIVIS cities. The data is derived from temperature data from May to September. The values are calculated from Landsat 8 data. The resolution is 100 m.</gco:CharacterString>
         </gmd:abstract>
         <gmd:purpose>
            <gco:CharacterString>The Urban Heat Island Effect of 2025 is used to visualise urban heat stress on an interactive dashboard.</gco:CharacterString>
         </gmd:purpose>
